sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as AuthenticationService
    participant DocProc as DocumentProcessor
    participant ContentMgr as ContentManagementService
    participant TextAnalysis as TextAnalysisEngine
    participant VoiceSynth as VoiceSynthesizer
    participant LearnGen as LearningContentGenerator
    participant BookCat as BookCatalogService
    participant ReadExp as ReadingExperienceService
    participant ConvAI as ConversationalAI
    participant Analytics as AnalyticsService
    
    %% Book Upload and Processing Flow
    User->>Client: Upload digital book
    Client->>API: POST /api/books/upload
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>DocProc: Process book file
    DocProc->>DocProc: Validate format
    DocProc->>DocProc: Extract text & structure
    DocProc->>ContentMgr: Store processed content
    ContentMgr-->>DocProc: Content stored
    DocProc-->>API: Processing complete
    
    API->>TextAnalysis: Analyze book content
    TextAnalysis->>TextAnalysis: Extract entities & themes
    TextAnalysis->>TextAnalysis: Assess complexity & readability
    TextAnalysis->>ContentMgr: Store analysis results
    ContentMgr-->>TextAnalysis: Results stored
    TextAnalysis-->>API: Analysis complete
    
    API->>VoiceSynth: Generate audio narration
    VoiceSynth->>VoiceSynth: Select appropriate voice
    VoiceSynth->>VoiceSynth: Generate audio segments
    VoiceSynth->>VoiceSynth: Create synchronization markers
    VoiceSynth->>ContentMgr: Store audio segments
    ContentMgr-->>VoiceSynth: Audio stored
    VoiceSynth-->>API: Audio generation complete
    
    API->>LearnGen: Generate learning materials
    LearnGen->>LearnGen: Create quizzes
    LearnGen->>LearnGen: Generate mind maps
    LearnGen->>LearnGen: Build flashcards
    LearnGen->>LearnGen: Create summaries
    LearnGen->>ContentMgr: Store learning materials
    ContentMgr-->>LearnGen: Materials stored
    LearnGen-->>API: Learning materials generated
    
    API->>BookCat: Update user's library
    BookCat->>BookCat: Add book to user's catalog
    BookCat-->>API: Library updated
    API-->>Client: Book processing complete
    Client-->>User: Notification: Book ready
    
    %% Reading and Learning Flow
    User->>Client: Select book from library
    Client->>API: GET /api/books/{bookId}
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>ReadExp: Request book content
    ReadExp->>ContentMgr: Get processed content
    ContentMgr-->>ReadExp: Return book content
    ReadExp->>ContentMgr: Get audio narration
    ContentMgr-->>ReadExp: Return audio data
    ReadExp->>ContentMgr: Get sync data
    ContentMgr-->>ReadExp: Return sync markers
    ReadExp->>ContentMgr: Get user annotations
    ContentMgr-->>ReadExp: Return annotations
    ReadExp-->>API: Return compiled book experience
    API-->>Client: Book content and resources
    Client-->>User: Display interactive book
    
    %% User Interaction with Content
    User->>Client: Toggle between reading/listening
    Client->>Client: Sync text highlighting with audio
    
    User->>Client: Create annotation
    Client->>API: POST /api/books/{bookId}/annotations
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>ContentMgr: Store annotation
    ContentMgr-->>API: Annotation stored
    API-->>Client: Annotation created
    Client-->>User: Display annotation
    
    User->>Client: Access learning tools
    Client->>API: GET /api/books/{bookId}/learning
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>ContentMgr: Get learning materials
    ContentMgr-->>API: Return materials
    API-->>Client: Learning materials
    Client-->>User: Display quizzes, mind maps, etc.
    
    %% Conversation with AI
    User->>Client: Ask question about book
    Client->>API: POST /api/books/{bookId}/conversation
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>ConvAI: Process user query
    ConvAI->>ContentMgr: Get book context
    ContentMgr-->>ConvAI: Return relevant content
    ConvAI->>ConvAI: Generate response
    ConvAI-->>API: AI response
    API-->>Client: Conversation response
    Client-->>User: Display AI answer
    
    %% Social and Sharing
    User->>Client: Share annotation with book club
    Client->>API: PUT /api/annotations/{annotationId}/share
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>ContentMgr: Update sharing permissions
    ContentMgr-->>API: Permissions updated
    API-->>Client: Sharing successful
    Client-->>User: Confirmation message
    
    %% Analytics Tracking
    Client->>API: POST /api/analytics/event
    API->>Analytics: Record user interaction
    Analytics->>Analytics: Process event data
    Analytics->>ContentMgr: Store analytics data
    ContentMgr-->>Analytics: Data stored
    Analytics-->>API: Analytics recorded
    
    %% Book Club and Discussion
    User->>Client: Create book club meeting
    Client->>API: POST /api/bookclubs/{clubId}/meetings
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>ContentMgr: Store meeting details
    ContentMgr-->>API: Meeting created
    API-->>Client: Meeting scheduled
    Client-->>User: Confirmation & calendar invite
    
    %% Language Learning (Phase 2+)
    User->>Client: Enable language learning for book
    Client->>API: POST /api/books/{bookId}/language-learning
    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Authentication successful
    API->>LearnGen: Generate language exercises
    LearnGen->>TextAnalysis: Analyze grammar structures
    TextAnalysis-->>LearnGen: Grammar analysis
    LearnGen->>LearnGen: Create pronunciation exercises
    LearnGen->>LearnGen: Build vocabulary lists
    LearnGen->>ContentMgr: Store language learning materials
    ContentMgr-->>LearnGen: Materials stored
    LearnGen-->>API: Language materials ready
    API-->>Client: Language learning enabled
    Client-->>User: Language learning interface